Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.22,0:00:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Quill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Parchment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Extra ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Extra-extra ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that everything on the checklist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yep!\N-Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.19,0:00:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we've completed the checklist\Nof things we need to create a checklist...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...we can make my checklist of the things\NI have to get done by the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.22,0:00:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Item 1: Create checklist of the things\NI have to accomplish by the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we doing, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.34,0:01:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already dropped off\Nyour cape at the cleaner's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...returned the blackboard\Nyou borrowed from Cheerilee...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...ordered new parchment and quills\Nfrom the stationery shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Seems like we just placed\Nan order for those a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.41,0:01:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can imagine why we go\Nthrough so many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like we're ahead\Nof schedule. What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Cupcakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I only ordered twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had an extra, so I though\NI'd make it a baker's dozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was very thoughtful of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just some of the icing\Nfrom the extra cupcake...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...is getting all over\Nthe one next to it. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I'm planning on\Nsharing these at a picnic later...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I don't want anypony to feel like\Nsomepony else is getting more icing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... no, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just move some of this one to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I think I may have\Nscooped too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops! Now those two have more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just try this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... No, that won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me just... hmm...\Nput some here, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not right. A little more\Non this one, a little bit... wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just... Ooh, a little bit\Nhere... here... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, oh yes. Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Time to tackle\Nthe next item on our...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're gonna have to add\N"Give a baby dragon a bath" to our list.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Very efficient! And a little bit gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like that's everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Triple-check checklist to make sure\Nwe didn't miss anything..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"...when the double-checked\Nthe checklist".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been holding that quill so long\NI've got a claw cramp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing we don't have anything\Nto report to Princess Celestia this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can write another word.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't sent a letter\Nto Princess Celestia this week?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad?! BAD?! Of course it's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to send Princess\NCelestia a letter every week...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...telling her about a lesson\NI've learned about friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not every other week.\NNot every ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Every! Single! Week!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my calendar?!\NWhere's my calendar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where it always is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When did we send the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Last Tuesday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And today is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuesday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonononononono...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't send her a letter\Nby sundown, I'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,TARDY!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tar-dy, Spike. Late! I'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how could I've let this happen?\NI'm usually so organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been late for an assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please! You're the most\Nstudious student ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the princess will forgive you\Nif you miss one little deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid to take that chance, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ruler of all of Equestria\Nwe're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The pony who holds\Nmy fate in her hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she doesn't forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't think she...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What if instead she starts thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm not taking my studies\Non friendship seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would she...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she makes me come back to\NCanterlot and puts me back in school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...and makes me *prove* I've been\Ntaking them seriously by giving me a task?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I don't pass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-But why wouldn't you pass...\N-She's my teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what teachers do\Nto students who don't pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,THEY SEND THEM BACK A GRADE!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But she won't just send me back a grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll send me back to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...magic kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the most ridiculous\Nthing I've ever heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna be sent back\Nto magic kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I have no reason to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm going to solve\Na friend's problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...and get that letter to Princess\NCelestia before sundown!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Got any problems, troubles, conundrums\Nor any other sort of issues...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...major or minor, that I as a good\Nfriend could help you solve?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I got nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it looks like I'm gonna have to\Nfind somepony who does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't end well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got this, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have plenty of time to\Nget that letter to Princess Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Has to be somepony around here\Nwho needs the help of a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Rarity! I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY, WHY, WHY?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the worst things\Nthat could happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...this is the! Worst! Possible! Thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened?! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost my diamond\Nencrusted purple ribbon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have searched HIGH!\NAnd I have searched low.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,LOW AND HIGH!\NHigh and low.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't find it anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,ANYWHERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I possibly finish\Nmy latest creation if I can't find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Never fear, Rarity. As your friend\NI'll do my best to help you fi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it always just\Nthe last place you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just lost your ribbon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...but now you've found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And nothing else is bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing that I as a good friend\Ncould help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,YES?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've left my measuring tape\Nunder the fabric over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you get that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Measuring tape. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight. Is there something bother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to panic.\NRarity is just one pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure one of my other\Nfriends will need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow must be angry with Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She must hate her guts. Oh, wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Rainbow. I know you're upset\Nwith Applejack, but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is that has\Ncome between you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm sure that I as a good friend\Ncan help you resolve your problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to hide\Nyour feelings from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you two must\Nhave had a terrible fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, why don't you tell me all\Nabout your issues with Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any issues with Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't? Then why are you\Ndestroying her property?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to put up a new barn, but\Nthis one's gotta come down first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get back to it, RD.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd take cover if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I've\Nwasted all that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have just come here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy always has some fear\Nshe's trying to get over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As a good friend\NI'll be able to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:09:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How can this be happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the days she had to stop being such\Na scaredy-pony she had to pick today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You really should have\Ncome to me sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You were carrying so much\Ntension in that shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It'll all be fine.\NToday isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But it will be over soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be all over! My time in Ponyville,\Nmy advanced studies...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. You're a good student.\NYou can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! But what if I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can! You just\Nhave to keep it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep! It! Together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking to... yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,SNAP OUT OF IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, I'm really worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean this letter thing\Nis really getting to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been so anxious all day that\Nyou've completely forgot about the picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just relax\Nand go hang out with...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The picnic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I should go see my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you've come to your senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me I did not forget the plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I did! I totally forgot them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the worst things\Nthat could happen, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The! Worst! Possible! Thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, why, why!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't expect me to\Nlay on the grass, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right, hun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:11:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the most terrific trouble\NI've ever been in...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I really, really,\Nreally need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,YES?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My letter to Princess Celestia\Nis almost overdue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I haven't learned\Nanything about friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness. I thought\Nsomething really awful had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Something awful HAS happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't turn in the letter\Non time, I'll be tardy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,TAAARDY!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No offense, sugar cube...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it looks like somepony's gettin'\Nthemselves all worked up over nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not nothing.\NThis is everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you guys to help me find somepony\Nwith a problem I can fix before sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,MY WHOLE LIFE DEPENDS ON IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Twilight. You're such a crackup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat and stop\Nsweatin' small stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. I've never seen\NTwilight so upset before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, what a drama queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Relatively speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Clock is ticking, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Clock... is... ticking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't find a friendship problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll *make* a friendship problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hai, gurls!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Hi, Twilight. How's it goi..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Guh-reat! Just great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You three look like\Nyou're doing great too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like three good\Nfriends who obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't need the help\Nof another good friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Smarty Pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She was mine when I was your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I want to give her to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... She's... great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like her... mane?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She even comes with\Nher own notebook and quill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,For when you want to pretend\Nshe's doing her homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's, um... great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like her... mane?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope the fact that\Nthere are three of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...and only one of her\Ndoesn't become a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to cause a rift\Nbetween such good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So who wants to play with her first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... You should play\Nwith her first, Sweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, cause you\Nlike her mane so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nononononono.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Scootaloo should\Nget to play with her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to, but, um...\NYou take her, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack says it's important to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to think of something.\NThinkthinkthink, Twilight, think!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, you're going to like Smarty Pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're going to like her\Nmore than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like her mane!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The "want it, need it" spell.\NWorks every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. Let's break it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you can all see that\Nthere is an important lesson...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...to be learned here about...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls. We're all friends here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you have to share?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Big McIntosh! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta help me get that\Ndoll away from those girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much. Now if\Nyou could just give her to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nnnope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all the commotion about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fighting over that doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That incredible, amazing doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't get a clear shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nnnope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'all hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the name of all things\Noats 'n apples is goin' on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-DON'T LOOK AT IT!\N-Don't look at what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My Smarty Pants doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I enchanted her and now\Neverypony is fighting over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you enchant your doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I had to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I had nothing to report to Princess Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought if I couldn't find\Na problem, I'd make a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The day is almost over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, Nelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet me in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, girls. If you care to visit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll be in magic kindergarten\Nback in Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-Magic kindergarten?\N-Canterlot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We're never gonna see Twilight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do, y'all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the worst things\Nthat could happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...this is the! Worst! Possible! Thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I really mean it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But... I'm supposed to send you\Na letter about friendship every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bad student. I'm tardy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a wonderful student, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to get a letter\Nevery week to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't punish her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't her fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, your highness.\NWe all saw that Twilight was upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But we thought that the thing\Nshe was worrying about...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...wasn't worth worrying about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So when she ran out all worked up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...not a single one of us\Ntried to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As Twilight's good friends,\Nwe should have taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...her feelings seriously\Nand been there for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't take her away from us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...just because we were\Ntoo insensitive to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you all learned\Na pretty valuable lesson today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I'll forget Twilight's\Npunishment on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,From this day forth\NI would like you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...to report to me your findings\Non the magic of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When and only when you happen to discover them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know I was in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend Spike made me aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you were letting\Nyour fears get the best of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I commend him for taking\Nyour feelings seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you will all excuse me,\NI must return to Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm expecting some mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'all heard the princess.\NSpike, take a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Princess Celestia.\NWe're writin' to you..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"...because today we all learned\Na little somethin' about friendship."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"We learned that you should take\Nyour friends' worries seriously."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Even if you don't think that\Nshe has anything to worry about."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"And that you shouldn't let\Nyour worries turn a small problem..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"...into an enormously huge\Nentire-town-in-total-chaos..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"...Princess-has-to-come-\N-and-save-the-day problem."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Signed, your loyal subjects."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"PS. Obviously Spike did not\Nhave to learn a lesson..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"...because he is the best, most\Nawesome friend a pony could ask for."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Unlike everypony else,\Nhe took things seriously. And..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just, um...
